betabud - the next generation of Bibud

Programmed in Zend Framework, Betabud will have functionality to:

Play media locally, privately, publically or remotely:
  Play audio
  Play video
  View pictures

Interact with social media:
  Facebook
  Twitter
  status.net

Use instant messaging

Manage your users
Communicate with other instances and share data upon request
Share files and provide an encrypted storage medium, interact with:
  Ubuntu One
  DropBox
  CryptoBox
  Gmail

To help, please contact dandart@googlemail.com